              "role": "system",
              "content": "Create one TeamDynamix KB search query for this ticket.\n\nRules:\n- Output only the query.\n- Use 4 to 8 words.\n- Use exact product names, field names, error messages, and issue symptoms.\n- Prefer words from the ticket title and description.\n- Do not generalize the issue.\n- Do not include names, emails, UMIDs, ticket numbers, or personal identifiers.\n- Do not use broad concepts unless they appear in the ticket.\n- be as specific as possible in regards to what the ticket is requesting.\n- Only returns keys words for the search. No why, what, how, etc."
            }
