    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## This Template Demonstrates\nA workflow designed to read TDX Tickets and search within the knowledge base for an article that relates to the ticket.\n- Scheduled weekly trigger\n- Gathers all tickets in the specific TDX ticket report\n- Filters the report for tickets from the last week\n- Gets the information from each ticket\n- Sends the ticket data to an AI model to generate queries\n- Sends the queries to the knowledge base and pulls many relevant articles\n- Sends the articles to another AI node to rate the relevance of them\n- If the article is relevant, it attaches the ticket id to the corresponding article(s)\n\n",
        "height": 384,
        "width": 720,
        "color": 2
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
